@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Quality Assurance";
}

<div class="container">
    <h1>Quality Assurance</h1>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>Our Quality Commitment</h3>
        <p>At our company, quality is not just a process - it's a culture. We implement stringent quality control measures at every stage of production to ensure our garments meet the highest international standards.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>Quality Control Process</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <strong>Fabric Inspection</strong>
                <p>All incoming fabrics are inspected for defects before being approved for production.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>In-Process Quality Checks</strong>
                <p>Our quality control team monitors production at every stage to identify and correct issues immediately.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Final Inspection</strong>
                <p>Each garment undergoes a thorough final inspection before packaging.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Random Sampling</strong>
                <p>Additional random sampling is conducted to verify consistent quality across the entire order.</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>Quality Standards</h3>
        <p>Our products comply with the following standards:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>AQL (Acceptable Quality Level) 2.5 for major defects</li>
            <li>ISO 9001 certified processes</li>
            <li>OEKO-TEX certified fabrics available upon request</li>
            <li>Compliance with international safety and chemical regulations</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
        <h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
        <p>We are committed to continuous quality improvement through:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Regular staff training</li>
            <li>Investment in modern technology</li>
            <li>Customer feedback analysis</li>
            <li>Benchmarking against industry best practices</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>